profile: Capital Asphalt and Interlock is family owned and operated by brothers, Derek & Kendall. Established in 1993, serving Arnprior and area, and Ottawa West and outlying areas we have established ourselves as residential paving experts. Our quality and workmanship is often imitated, but never duplicated. We have continuously  taken great pride in setting and maintaining the highest of standards in residential paving and landscaping over our 25+ years in business, on each and every project!  Team CAPITAL appreciates the opportunity to work with you! Contact us for a consultation - you'll be happy that you did!
